text: Mihaela Ciolacu (born 12 August 1998) is a Romanian footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Romania women's national team. ==Career== Ciolacu has been capped for the Romania national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian women's footballers Category:Romania women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:FCU Olimpia Cluj players
